paragraphs.title: Build the Decision Tree model
paragraphs.text:
%script

-- Build a classification model and then generate a lift test result and an apply result.

DECLARE
    v_setlst DBMS_DATA_MINING.SETTING_LIST;
    
BEGIN
    v_setlst('ALGO_NAME') := 'ALGO_DECISION_TREE';
    DBMS_DATA_MINING.CREATE_MODEL2(
        'N1_CLASS_MODEL',
        'CLASSIFICATION',
        'SELECT * FROM N1_TRAIN_DATA',
        v_setlst,
        'CUST_ID',
        'LTV_BIN');
END;
